title: Words and expressions which are not defined in these Regulations, shall have the same meaning or sen
clause_text: Words and expressions which are not defined in these Regulations, shall have the same meaning or sense as in the :- Maharashtra Municipal Councils, Nagar Panchayats and Industrial Townships Act, 1965; Maharashtra Metropolitan Region Development Authority Act, 2016; Real Estate (Regulation and Development) Act, 2016; Maharashtra Housing and Area Development Act, 1976; Maharashtra Slum Areas (Improvement, Clearance And Redevelopment) Act, 1971. Act - means the Maharashtra Regional & Town Planning Act, 1966 as may be amended from time to time.
